# Helpful commands:
# `ghostty +show-config` ... shows the current config values
# `ghostty +show-config --default --docs` ... shows the default config values with documentation
# `ghostty +list-fonts` ... shows the list of available fonts
# `ghostty +list-themes` ... shows the list of available themes
# `ghostty +validate-config`... validates the current config

# Ghostty syntax support for Neovim (macOS)
# variant in share:
#   `cp -r /Applications/Ghostty.app/Contents/Resources/nvim/site ~/.local/share/nvim/`
# variant in config:
#   `cp -r /Applications/Ghostty.app/Contents/Resources/nvim/site/* ~/.config/nvim/after/`

